original_title: AKB48単独リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2016
overview: The AKB48 Tandoku Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2016 (AKB48 単独リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2016) was held from January 16 to January 18, 2016 at Tokyo Dome City Hall. Fans made their voices heard by voting for their favorite AKB48 original songs.
title: AKB48 Tandoku Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2016
